(3, 1, 'Bomber Bugs problem', 6, '', 1, '', 1, 0, 'These bugs are everywhere, you need to take care of that problem before they will spread all over the island and in return I’ll prepare another piece of armor for you.', 'Kill 5 Bomber Bugs', 'I’m glad to see you alive', -1, -1, -1, 2, -1, 'Chose which armor suits you best', 250, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, 10182, 1, 10188, 1, 10194, 1, -1, 0, 4, 45, 3, 120, 6, 55, -1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-03-17 22:29:31'),
(4, 1, 'Supplies for Blacksmith (Repeatable)', 0, '', 1, '', 1, 1, 'I need some of that rare items but there is small problem, it can be obtained only from these bigger types for Bomber Bugs. Beware they are more dangerous than the ones which you found before. In return I’ll give you another piece of armor.', 'Obtain 5 Bomber Bug Teeth', 'Good job, you handled to not die, that’s the good news, do you have my items ?', -1, -1, -1, 3, -1, 'Pick armor of your choice', 550, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, 10186, 1, 10192, 1, 10198, 1, -1, 0, 4, 55, 3, 350, 6, 65, -1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5, 1, 'Reconnaissance', 6, '', 1, '', 1, 0, 'Head the road to the coast and check if it’s safe.', 'Make reconnaissance', 'Is it safe?', -1, -1, -1, 4, -1, 'Great that you checked it for me, here is your reward', 750, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, 10185, 1, 10191, 1, 10197, 1, -1, 0, 4, 75, 3, 450, 6, 85, -1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-03-12 15:31:55'),
(6, 1, 'Mysterious passage', 6, '', 1, '', 1, 0, 'Pass through mysterious passage and kill all bugs which you will find.', 'Pass through mysterious passage and kill all bugs which you will find', 'Were you able to defeat them all ?', -1, -1, -1, 5, -1, 'Excellent, here is your reward', 1500, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, 10184, 1, 10190, 1, 10196, 1, -1, 0, 4, 85, 3, 1250, -1, 0, -1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7, 1, 'Bomber Bug hive (Group)', 0, '', 1, '', 1, 1, 'We finally know where is their hive. Probably they have something like Bomber Bug Queen which you need to take care but first you need to gather a group as you won’t be able to defeat her alone.', 'Head to Bomber Bug Hive and kill their Queen', 'Is it possible, were you able to handle that impossible task ?', -1, -1, -1, 6, -1, 'Excellent, here is your reward', 2500, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, -1, 0, 20004, 1, 20005, 1, 20006, 1, -1, 0, 4, 95, 3, 1500, -1, 0, -1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');

